</p><note class="- topic/note " id="GUID-A88FC9AE-28B9-4C44-B5EC-648ADEEE46DA"><p class="- topic/p "> Certain images may show variations due to their origin from the Colorado 1650.
</p></note></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-F9610346-305D-4109-8480-42E46C2A7EF1" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul compact="no" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_250A7C8513614E659F239E5B8299E070" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Side cutter or knife 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T30 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T25 
</p></li><li id="LI_911FF6CBAF21426EB1AC931E1B20BE38" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T10 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open ended spanner 19 mm or Allen key wrench 6 mm 
</p></li><li id="LI_92C04D314810460FB960B453040379FA" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Spanner 7 mm 
</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves : 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-DB340B14-87E5-4FDB-8108-245D16C84FF1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-94C20406-75A1-4BD0-A7DB-8CD9777F04B0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Install the transport locking material </title><table id="NEW" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the 2 screws of the power supply unit at the roll drawer side. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_4E4AB683478741658561589BAC5064A5" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-8E06318B-706A-4951-89A4-C93FE787ACF7-low.png" id="IMAGE_31F786EDC47B4CB2A38B2BBA321D1066" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-8E06318B-706A-4951-89A4-C93FE787ACF7-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_3C21FD3D972E4037A4F89EF98F9DC5C2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-51BB3BB7-4B84-4231-BBB4-05F61956CE0E-low.png" id="IMAGE_87839D61D09A4ED1A5C110FE41AE0DD3" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-51BB3BB7-4B84-4231-BBB4-05F61956CE0E-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_732A40465F6F4AF28415C164D96780F8" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-672343E9-CF3F-4688-82CC-EC91AB56A562-low.png" id="IMAGE_261ED8814DDE41778A03F2AA741CBCD9" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-672343E9-CF3F-4688-82CC-EC91AB56A562-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Open the maintenance unit and install the foam and tape. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-1D5534A7-26A7-47FC-9359-A6E207ADC68A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-614DEE36-A666-4990-98A7-61BDDCDE2C1A-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-614DEE36-A666-4990-98A7-61BDDCDE2C1A-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "><draft-comment translate="no" class="- topic/draft-comment ">icoontje install tape</draft-comment>
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the chiller unit. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the ink hand ling unit. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the media drawer. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_872D9BAD372E42C1A3426BEEA0949E92" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-3804AB96-7058-49D7-8D88-11B4BDA69057-low.png" id="IMAGE_8E9E419609254DE7B83A9E8012E79B4D" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3804AB96-7058-49D7-8D88-11B4BDA69057-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the cover in the media drawer. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Install 4 cable ties of the roll cores and 2 at the locking handle of the vertical transport.. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-A8F7280B-A15C-499B-AA21-6BD2991435D6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-2E9B5B4D-4676-4BDC-B5BA-FB596B5AEEF9-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-2E9B5B4D-4676-4BDC-B5BA-FB596B5AEEF9-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-C8737EDA-C551-4057-AC74-6DDDC8AEE15C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-73413FBE-7DBC-4321-A9C2-91E1D25741B2-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-73413FBE-7DBC-4321-A9C2-91E1D25741B2-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-1E66FEF9-4410-40B2-8031-28B6F0BECD5B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-49345F90-C7FD-4F12-AAB4-B427EA671CCA-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-49345F90-C7FD-4F12-AAB4-B427EA671CCA-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Mount the media drawer locking plates in reverse position. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_9658EC70D79F422F907E79FE59631A51" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-756565A1-3885-4C57-BDAE-06968B66A47E-low.png" id="IMAGE_BED59CDDD2E848B9BE3B67DAE616E620" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-756565A1-3885-4C57-BDAE-06968B66A47E-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_2324AE4B0E8F4060AB48D350841A531F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D3B0536D-BF9E-4F2E-98E8-B9E6E94D148D-low.png" id="IMAGE_2593713CD01D4FEEB9D713D955201611" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D3B0536D-BF9E-4F2E-98E8-B9E6E94D148D-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_969400BD42A84E7C9EE8E51F0F1D0180" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-668C1FBE-7BA4-41F1-A028-40B564804830-low.png" id="IMAGE_A7346236CD3A4770969237E52BFD497F" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-668C1FBE-7BA4-41F1-A028-40B564804830-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_D81FCC53C125414C8BC47573389857FE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-BEC93BE3-0B32-42CD-9C22-D3E6429B27A7-low.png" id="IMAGE_3F3A2BF47B4D4D52BEBC9D5F60F9AF1F" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-BEC93BE3-0B32-42CD-9C22-D3E6429B27A7-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Close the media drawer. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the 2 screws of the media drawer locking mechanism (at the ink handling side). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_5A36AED061684AACB8435FC4A1BF5DA8" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-35F0564F-648F-4CF6-ABA1-632AF4BBA307-low.png" id="IMAGE_304B0BB3AD0C4FD19FEA2677512B1547" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-35F0564F-648F-4CF6-ABA1-632AF4BBA307-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the 2 screws of the media drawer locking mechanism (at the chiller side). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-95AEBDF5-46D6-47C3-9A75-77A5CCF29FE6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-7123441D-6DD1-4D6A-99B6-87D49E2FFD69-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7123441D-6DD1-4D6A-99B6-87D49E2FFD69-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-33397131-7A8B-4392-80FB-C98A24888573" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6A93A2E8-9B8E-4363-A0CE-867B95E3F2CD-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6A93A2E8-9B8E-4363-A0CE-867B95E3F2CD-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the 2 foam blocks below the ink containers. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_111FC9043AC14793A91A883D9044A9B8" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FF1489CC-3651-42C2-AA49-5BF10E6757C9-low.png" id="IMAGE_A1C0F5CAF12640178DD3A5B606FFEA6F" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FF1489CC-3651-42C2-AA49-5BF10E6757C9-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">12 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Close and lock the ink handling unit. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_DE664ACB06F34D668575855FBB4D8C46" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D9F63DFF-C239-4B4A-87B1-94D52C6D919F-low.png" id="IMAGE_C151F1EDAA0E4488BEF0DC1A8EC45B7F" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D9F63DFF-C239-4B4A-87B1-94D52C6D919F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">13 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the cover below the knife compartment (1 screw). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_43F2C9AED6984867932E3044F750E6F9" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D7E97970-1566-4A5F-A623-6D8C802C37DB-low.png" id="IMAGE_AEFCC993485D4B858CADED31C267BF23" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D7E97970-1566-4A5F-A623-6D8C802C37DB-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">14 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the cover of the knife compartment (1 screw). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-4306F490-E90E-4A63-B14D-377ECD294D2C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-058D1379-0DD6-4E67-B04C-B72BD8BB80B9-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-058D1379-0DD6-4E67-B04C-B72BD8BB80B9-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">15 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the tie-rap from the ink handling unit hinge. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-FF02A0EE-4C8B-4367-8581-074012A12331" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-09C1545F-256D-47D6-A341-2638078305A0-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-09C1545F-256D-47D6-A341-2638078305A0-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">16 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lock the chiller unit. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_81F5CC3B7ECC444B850727BEFA46FFAE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-19C0014A-D385-4F71-AC6C-C99E84439041-low.png" id="IMAGE_9B31584C4F504668A8E5E72D53A3792A" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-19C0014A-D385-4F71-AC6C-C99E84439041-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">17 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Mount the cable ties on the chiller hinge. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_D99CF5FA305540C0837C299C023B3B27" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1961202D-6FF5-4C7C-AB97-298D42F4F060-low.png" id="IMAGE_2BE63008194B4900B2C61D31C51E5877" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1961202D-6FF5-4C7C-AB97-298D42F4F060-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">18 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the cover (below the user panel next to the chiller). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_98CBA0C370C6481C821F859F46011743" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C8806A16-9A34-43A8-BC74-0840FA179DC9-low.png" id="IMAGE_27124DBD49AA4009A5179261695E93DA" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C8806A16-9A34-43A8-BC74-0840FA179DC9-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">19 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the foam strips (2x) and tape. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_8A899FF5FB504EDD92FA902551E171BE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-467405CE-6CA4-400E-88DC-84BC1D898C19-low.png" id="IMAGE_AC751B9F30B34936BFD78B63B2FBAB8B" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-467405CE-6CA4-400E-88DC-84BC1D898C19-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_DD7F98B25E474442BDE4216FD38EDF9B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-15A7F6CA-3FC0-4B81-A52F-1E567305B1A6-low.png" id="IMAGE_38A03A3A7D494607BB2147C86801B0EC" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-15A7F6CA-3FC0-4B81-A52F-1E567305B1A6-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_C4A230CC589E47678DB15C6E4D237CB2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B94461D5-5E93-4F49-9E00-4A6E4A10BA19-low.png" id="IMAGE_527DE0DB1A5F4CE38C3E8BB6941B0EBE" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B94461D5-5E93-4F49-9E00-4A6E4A10BA19-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">20 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Put the cables of the operator panel in a plastic bag and tape it . 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_234D4200715440F28C3E003440F576F5" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-ABE99F5D-9CCA-4FBF-8661-189C6FA8EDF2-low.png" id="IMAGE_F9420D5F44AE49069A21900EE8DD1927" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-ABE99F5D-9CCA-4FBF-8661-189C6FA8EDF2-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">21 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the wider drive at the left and right hand side (4 nuts and 1 or 2 connectors). 
