</p></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_EE50B389AF714C0191B6967974885BE4" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-EC41671C-3B5F-42AB-8F86-E4327D52D4D7-low.png" id="IMAGE_FDE99023CCA247379879E616C5C212AF" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-EC41671C-3B5F-42AB-8F86-E4327D52D4D7-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">30 
