</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Close the top cover. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">43 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lock with 2 screws of the top cover to the transport locking mechanism. 
